OwnershipTransferred(address,address).details: This emits when ownership of a contract changes.

InterfaceAdded(bytes4).notice: Emitted when an interface is added to the contract via `_addInterface`.

InterfaceRemoved(bytes4).notice: Emitted when an interface is removed from the contract via `_removeInterface`.

getSpaceById(string).notice: Returns the address of a space by its spaceId
